== 7...Qc7 ==
Black develops the queen to c7 in order to prepare e5. This will likely lead to the Carlsbad variation.

White's main response is [[/8. g3|'''8. g3''']] preparing to develop the dark-squared bishop to f4 where it can put pressure on the knight after '''8...e5 9. dxe5 Nxe5'''. This also prepares to fianchetto the light-squared bishop.

